elements.title: Supernova (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Access your design system and everything that comes with it - Tokens, Assets, Components, even your entire documentation site. Use what you find directly in your tools, without switching context.

elements.title: DLmoji (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Semantic search for Emojis, powered by Deep Learning and intelligent APIs

elements.title: esa Search (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Search for posts by your team's esa. No official esa.io product.

elements.title: FileZilla (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Connect to the FTP/SFTP server via FileZilla by just using your keyboard!

elements.title: Statamic Documentation Search (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: This extension allows you to search through the Statamic docs directly from Raycast.

elements.title: Monse - Banking In Raycast (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Connect your bank account and see latest incomes, expenses, and details.

elements.title: ColorSlurp (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Control ColorSlurp's color picker features from Raycast

elements.title: YouTube Music (Raycast Store)
elements.contents: Control the YouTube Music tab in browser with your keyboard.
